short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple extension to open the current page in Google Page Speed Insights.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Open in Google Page Speed Insights Chrome extension provides a single click way to analyze the speed and optimization of any webpage you're browsing.

With this handy tool, you can effortlessly access Google's Page Speed Insights directly from your browser. No more manual copying and pasting URLs into separate tabs â€“ simply click on the extension icon, and instantly receive valuable insights into your page's performance.

Key Features:

1. 1-click open in google page speed insights.
2. Very lightweight.
